This article is a letter from President Barack Obama to the Speaker of the House, regarding the continuation of the national emergency with respect to weapons of mass destruction. The letter states that according to the National Emergencies Act, a national emergency will automatically terminate unless the President publishes a notice stating that it is to continue beyond the anniversary date. President Obama has sent a notice to the Federal Register, stating that the national emergency with respect to the proliferation of weapons of mass destruction will continue for 1 year beyond November 14, 2012.